Quick hack to list packages in a given repositories

Note: tuples can include distro:release:source to lits source packages:
./list_packages.py http://repos.ros.org/repos/ros_bootstrap/ --os-name-and-os-code-name-and-arch-tuples ubuntu:xenial:amd64 
./list_packages.py http://repos.ros.org/repos/ros_bootstrap/ --os-name-and-os-code-name-and-arch-tuples ubuntu:xenial:source

